t_01.jpg','application/octet-stream',41550,488,'My graduation project aimed at designing tile forms for the company Brix, at Milan. The company’s brief stated a main tile module representing a pattern to which the design approach adds value. The design had to be two\r\ndimensional, in stoneware ceramic. \r\n\r\nFlux simulates the random and chaotic patterns of nature and brings it to the indoor landscape, where people can experience the same unpredictability of nature. The tile module will act as a brigde between the domestic order and the organic disorder.\r\n\r\nDomus Academy . MD 2010 . Master Project . Guide | Eliana Lorena, Massimo Nadalini, Claudio Laviola . November 2010 ','Work',NULL),(2008,NULL,'2011-09-16 05:01:37','2011-09-16 06:30:53','d_kaur_vineet_02.jpg','application/octet-stream',86681,488,'Domus Academy . MD 2010 . Master Project . Guide | Eliana Lorena, Massimo Nadalini, Claudio Laviola . November 2010 ','Work',NULL),(2009,NULL,'2011-09-16 05:01:52','2011-09-16 06:30:54','d_kaur_vineet_03.jpg','application/octet-stream',117975,488,'Domus Academy . MD 2010 . Master Project . Guide | Eliana Lorena, Massimo Nadalini, Claudio Laviola . November 2010 ','Work',NULL),(2013,NULL,'2011-09-16 05:12:39','2011-09-16 06:30:55','d5_ecospy_01.jpg','application/octet-stream',96847,488,'EcoSpy is a game to instill children an effective awareness of their energy consumption in the household. By using the metaphor of a daily household check-up, children can be \"in charge\" of monitoring energy use at home and take action. They can also play with other children and compare their household overall results among other actions.','Work',NULL),(2014,NULL,'2011-09-16 05:22:01','2011-09-16 06:30:56','d_3_musa_03.jpg','application/octet-stream',187912,488,'Musa is a collapsible shelter for the illegal\r\nimmigrants.It aims at camouflaging them as well\r\nas giving them a respectable earning to sustain their families in their native country.\r\nThe shelter comes with a self i