tructures. From previous work experience at ‘Indooria Glasses’, I have good understanding of the glass furniture\r\n\r\nIf I could get an opportunity to be a part of the company as trainee for Internship and diploma, I can learn technological side of the product, I will be thankful to you. I am committing you the best of my knowledge what I have gained in NID & my sincerity.\r\n\r\nExpecting your response, cooperation and guidance,\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\nSanjay Kumar\r\nLifestyle accessory design\r\nNational institute of design, Ahmadabad \r\nContect:sanjay_k@nid.edu\r\nmob.no:09712236984\r\n','http://','http://','2010-10-12 12:03:36','2010-10-12 12:03:36','resume.pdf_final.pdf','application/pdf',254126,'portfolio_final.pdf','application/pdf',2144862,0,'6c330f40',61,NULL),(106,'rajesh','rajesh.13kits@gmail.com','UI Deziner','Dear\r\nTrue Sparrow systems.\r\n\r\nThis is B.Rajesh form hyderabad . you can find my portfolio in the following link . please revert me if i am eligible for ur post \r\n\r\ncheers\r\nRajesh','http://','http://www.dezineconnect.com/portfolios/show/237','2010-10-12 22:07:36','2010-10-12 22:07:55',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'108ae3d7',67,NULL),(107,'SONALI JAGDALE','jagdale_1sonali@yahoo.co.in','FASHION DESIGNING & GRAPHIC DESIGNING','RESPECTED SIR / MAME,\r\n            I AM LOOKING TO FIND A JOB IN MUMBAI AS A FASHION DESIGNER.\r\nI HAVE VERY GOOD KNOWLEDGE IN GARMENT DESIGNING, COLOR COMBINATIONS & PRE-PRODUCTION SAMPLE DESIGNING.\r\n            PLEASE CHECK MY ATTACHING C.V. FILE. I AM WAITING FOR YOUR IMPORTANT REPLY.\r\nTHANKS,\r\nREGARDS,\r\nSONALI JAGDALE','http://','http://','2010-10-13 04:29:57','2010-10-13 04:39:44','NEW_RESUME-_SONALI.doc','application/msword',75264,'SONALI_S_DESIGN_PRESENTETION.pptx','application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.presentationml.presentation',17103423,1,'400884a7',65,NULL),(108,'Kriti Chaudhary','kriti.utopia@gmail.com','Product/ Interior Designer','','http://','http://','2010-10-16 15:41:26','2010